## 3) Ingestion service (`apps/ingestion-service`)

### 3.1 Endpoints

- `GET /health`
- `POST /documents`
- `GET /documents/{document_id}`
- `GET /documents/{document_id}/sections`
- `GET /metrics`

### 3.2 Upload modes

`POST /documents` supports:

1. multipart form-data (`file`)
2. raw body upload when `Content-Type` is `application/pdf` or `application/octet-stream` (+ optional `X-Filename`)

Validation behavior:

- 422 if no valid file payload
- 400 if filename is missing or not `.pdf`
- parse failure is persisted as `Document(status="failed", error_message=...)` and returned as HTTP 422

### 3.3 Parsing behavior (`services/parser.py`)

- PyMuPDF text extraction page-by-page
- line cleanup and noise rejection (page markers, file-path-like lines, punctuation fragments, very short noise)
- heading detection via numeric + title-case heuristics
- inline heading/body splitting and embedded numbered heading extraction
- repeated short cross-page boilerplate stripping
- per-section page range tracking (`page_start`, `page_end`)
- fallback section if structure detection is weak

### 3.4 Persistence model

- `Document`: id/title/filename/status/error_message/created_at
- `Section`: id/document_id/order/title/content/page_start/page_end

