## 9) Export contract and report generation (`services/reports.py`)

### 9.1 Canonical export dataset

`final_exported_findings(...)` currently enforces:

- `artifact_role == "publishable_finding"`
- `publication_state == "publishable"`
- excludes ledger/system bookkeeping rows

### 9.2 Export contract

`build_export_contract(...)` provides:

- dataset identity
- export allowance + blockers
- counts by status
- finding IDs (document-wide vs section)
- generation metadata + schema version

### 9.3 PDF generation

- custom low-level PDF writer (no heavy external PDF generation dependency at output stage)
- line wrapping, bullet support, safe character normalization
- user-safe text sanitization that strips internal pipeline terms

