## 10) Frontend behavior (`apps/frontend/src`)

Routes:

- `/` upload
- `/sections` section review + start audit
- `/findings` findings/review/analysis workspace
- `/report` report center

API layer (`src/lib/api.ts`) uses ingestion + orchestration base URLs and XHR upload progress reporting.

Presentation layer (`src/lib/presentation.ts`) performs normalization/sanitization and parity-style checks used by UI contract testing.

